    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243890/extras/0008cbbbafc81b8007611229e39b1c09.poster.avif?t=1769245213\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243890/extras/0008cbbbafc81b8007611229e39b1c09.webm?t=1769245213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243890/extras/0008cbbbafc81b8007611229e39b1c09.mp4?t=1769245213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《A Simpler World》是一款温馨舒适的小型建造游戏，专注于创造力与放松体验。从荒芜的岛屿开始，清理环境，打造属于你的小小家园。所有装饰道具从一开始就可使用，让你自由装点室内外空间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏没有既定目标，但若你一直渴望在迷人的像素艺术世界中放松身心，这或许正是你的理想之选！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有宠物哦！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏝️ <strong>随机生成岛屿：</strong>从多种随机生成的岛屿中选择建造之地</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ <strong>自由装饰：</strong>所有道具即刻解锁，无需任何解锁步骤</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦥 <strong>惬意体验：</strong>无目标无压力，只管放松身心创造美好</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐈 <strong>宠物系统：</strong>宠物！</p>",
